  "description": "Manages scope context for a logger instance using a stack-based approach.\nScopes are used to group related log entries and provide context information.\nThread-safe: Uses a stack per context value.",
  "title": "Class LoggerScope",
  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Core.LoggerScope' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Core.LoggerScope' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Core_LoggerScope'>Class LoggerScope    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Core/LoggerScope.cs#L40'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Core.html'>Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Core</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Core.LoggerScope.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Manages scope context for a logger instance using a stack-based approach.\nScopes are used to group related log entries and provide context information.\nThread-safe: Uses a stack per context value.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>internal sealed class LoggerScope : IDisposable</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Inheritance</h4><dl class=\"typelist inheritance\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object'>object</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Core.LoggerScope.html'>LoggerScope</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Implements</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.idisposable'>IDisposable</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Inherited Members</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object)'>object.Equals(object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object-system-object)'>object.Equals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gethashcode'>object.GetHashCode()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gettype'>object.GetType()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.referenceequals'>object.ReferenceEquals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.tostring'>object.ToString()</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Constructors</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Core.LoggerScope.#ctor(System.Object,System.Collections.Generic.Stack{System.Object},System.Action)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Core.LoggerScope.#ctor(System.Object,System.Collections.Generic.Stack{System.Object},System.Action)' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Core_LoggerScope__ctor_System_Object_System_Collections_Generic_Stack_System_Object__System_Action_'>LoggerScope(object, Stack&lt;object&gt;, Action)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Core/LoggerScope.cs#L63'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Core.LoggerScope.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Initializes a new instance of the LoggerScope class.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public LoggerScope(object scope, Stack&lt;object&gt; scopeStack, Action onDispose)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>scope</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object'>object</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Core.LoggerScope.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The scope to push.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>scopeStack</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.generic.stack-1'>Stack</a>&lt;<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object'>object</a>&gt;  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Core.LoggerScope.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">